Si kastaba ha ahaatee, cudurku si degdeg ah ayuu ugu faafay magaalooyinka, gobollada iyo wadamada deriska ah.
Bishii Janaayo 20, ayaa la soo saaray warbixin ay soo saareen shaqaalaha caafimaadka, oo soo jeedinaya in faafitaanka qof-qof uu yahay mid suurtagal ah.
Bishii Janaayo 23, Wuhan ayaa la xiray oo gaadiidka dadweynaha ayaa la joojiyay.
