In kasta oo SARS-CoV-2 uu yahay fayras cusub oo loogu talagalay aadanaha, haddana halista weyn ee SARS-CoV sida lagu soo sheegay 7 Janaayo 2020 waa inay u keento walaac weyn Shiinaha iyadoo la tixgelinayo qoto dheer ee uu ka qaatay cudurka SARS ee 2003.
Si kastaba ha noqotee, illaa 19 Janaayo 2020, agaasimaha Xarunta Xakamaynta Cudurrada ee Wuhan ayaa u tacsiyeeyey muwaadiniinta isagoo sheegay in fayraska cusub ee coronavirus uu leeyahay heerar hoose oo gudbinta iyo heerarka taranka oo aad u hooseeya oo aan wax dhibaato ah ku lahayn ka hortagga iyo xakamaynta cudurka.
