Bedelka bAngiotensin enzyme 2 (ACE2) waa enzyme ku xiran dusha sare (membranes cell) ee unugyada sanbabada, wadnaha, kelyaha, iyo xiidmaha.
ACE2 waxay xakameysaa waxqabadka enzyme-ka la xiriira (ACE) iyadoo la yareynayo heerarka angiotensin-II iyo kor u qaadista Ang (1-7) taasoo ka dhigaysa bartilmaameed muhiim u ah daaweynta cudurada wadnaha. ACE2 sidoo kale waxay u shaqeysaa sidii waddo-galka unugyada ee qaar ka mid ah coronaviruses.
Nooca anzyme-ka ee aadanaha waxaa loo yaqaan hACE2.
Angiotensin 2 enzyme-ka wax-ku-ool ah waa zinc-ka oo ka kooban ironloenzyme oo ku yaal dusha sare ee unugyada endothelial iyo unugyada kale.
ACE2 protein wuxuu ka kooban yahay N-terminal peptidase M2 domain iyo C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 waa nooc ka mid ah borotiinka dhinaca xuubka ah ee loo yaqaan 'membrane protein', oo leh aag firfircoon oo enzymatically firfircoon oo soo bandhigaya dusha sare ee unugyada ku jira sanbabada iyo unugyada kale.
Qaybta unugyada ka baxsan ee ACE2 waxaa laga saaraa qaybta fayraska iyada oo loo marayo enzyme loo yaqaan 'blood-digestion', iyo borotiinka la kala-baxay ee ka dhasha ayaa lagu sii daayaa xididdada dhiigga oo ugu dambeyntii ku jira kaadida.
ACE2 waxay ku jirtaa xubnaha badankood: ACE2 waxay ku dhegan tahay maqaarka unugyada alveolar nooca II ee unugyada, enterocytes ee mindhicirka yar, dareemayaasha iyo unugyada wadnaha ee wadnaha iyo unugyada muruqyada jilicsan ee xubnaha badankood.
Calaamadaha ACE2 MRNA waxaa laga heli karaa maskaxda maskaxda, qanjidhada hypothalamus iyo briainstem.
Shaqada ugu horeysa ee ACE2 waa inay u istaagto sidii ay u noqon lahayd mid isku dheelitiran oo ku habboon ACE.
ACE waxay xakameyneysaa hormoonka angiotensin I ee ku jira angiotensin II oo vasoconstricting ah.
ACE2 waxay si isku xigta u nuugtaa amino acid phenylalanine oo ka soo jeeda carboxyl-terminal angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) waxayna ku biyo-saartaa angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 waxay tirtiri kartaa peptides kale oo ay ka mid yihiin [des-Arg9] -bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, iyo ghrelin.
ACE2 waxay sidoo kale xakameysaa wareejinta xuubka xuubka ee amino acid SLC6A19 oo ay weheliso cudurka Hartnup.
Sida borotiinka transmembrane, ACE2 waxay u shaqeysaa sidii marin muhiim ah oo unugyada u ah coronavirus-yada qaarkood, oo ay ku jiraan HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (fayraska sababa SARS); iyo SARS-CoV-2 (fayraska sababa COVID-19).
Xanuunkan oo la yiraahdo sars-cov1 iyo sars-cov2 ayaa isku daraya astaamaha ACE2 ee ku jira unugyada, taasoo keenta in endocytosis iyo translocation ee fayraska ay ku dhacaan unugyada.
Qalabka baaritaanka ee ay wadaagaan dhammaan nidaamyada S protein-ka ee ku saabsan borotiinka 'serine protease' TMPRSS2, iyo qaab dhismeedka kaas oo hadda loo tixgeliyo inuu yahay daaweynta ugu weyn. Tani waxay keentay hoos u dhaca heerka ACE2, ee unugyada, taasoo laga yaabo inay ka caawiso la dagaallanka cudurka.
Xitaa haddii ay ku dhacdo cudurro badan, waxaa loo baahan yahay in la sii wado daaweynta ka hortagga ACE-da ee ARB.
Baaritaan la sameeyay July 11, 2012 ayaa lagu ogaaday in ACE inhibitors-ku ay keeneen 34% hoos u dhac cudurka qaboobaha marka loo eego daawada.
